narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: German 140 is very text-driven, reading an entire novel, which is surprisingly fun and not too difficult. You go through a series of different themes and learn very different kinds of vocabulary. I'd recommend it, though the umbrella course is a big disorganized.
I would recommend this class to anyone interested in German culture, language, and/or history.
